#include &lt;math.h&gt;   // sqrt, pow
</code></pre>

Function Description <code>putchar(c)</code> Writes a single character <code>puts(str)</code> Writes a string and appends <code>\n</code> to the end <p>Example: </p><pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
int main() {
    putchar(‘A’);
    puts(“ Hello”);
    return 0;
}
